<h3>Usage</h3>

<h5>Design</h5>
<p> All style definitions can be found in <a href="https://github.com/kgrgreer/foam3/blob/development/src/foam/nanos/controller/AppStyles.js">foam3/src/foam/nanos/controller/AppStyles.js</a></p>
<table>
  <tr>
    <th>Font Type(CSS Class Name)</th>
    <th>Use for </th>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>H1(h100)</td>
    <td>Oversized tiles. Use in moderation. Max 1 per page</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>H2(h200)</td>
    <td>Main feature highlighting/Top level headers</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>H3(h300)</td>
    <td>Main title/Large section header</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>H4(h400)</td>
    <td>Most commonly used section headers</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>H5(h500)</td>
    <td>Sub-section headers/Group headings, often used in upper case to ensure visual heirarchy</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>H6(h600)</td>
    <td>Large labels/RO property labels/Button Labels</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Paragraph - Label(p-label)</td>
    <td>Read-Write form labels</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Paragraph - Large(p-lg)</td>
    <td>Use sparingly, mainly to create visual heirarchy</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Paragraph - Base(p)</td>
    <td>Most commonly used. Make sure to wrap all text in this</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Paragraph - SemiBold (p-semiBoold)</td>
    <td>Large labels/empasis text</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Paragraph - Bold(p-bold)</td>
    <td>Large labels/empasis text</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Paragraph - legalText(p-legal)</td>
    <td>Error messages or other fine text</td>
  </tr>
</table>

